headline: Wall Street Bulls Look Optimistic About CrowdStrike (CRWD): Should You Buy?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), CrowdStrike (CRWD) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: Fal.Con 2025: CrowdStrike and Partners Define the Future of Security Through Ecosystem Innovation
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, September 08, 2025--CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced that Fal.Con 2025 will feature a record 115+ sponsors, led by Amazon Web Services (AWS), Dell Technologies, Google Cloud, Intel, NVIDIA, and Salesforce. The four-day conference has reached capacity with more than 8,000+ attendees from 3,000 organizations across 65 countries.
